BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Emerging Topics: Pop-Up Talk
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260213
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260213
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51843707755944
DESCRIPTION:DataLab's pop-up talks are by DataLab faculty\, staff\, and af
 filiates and focus on emerging topics\, tips\, and trends in data science.
  Join us for the Winter 2026 series on alternating Fridays from 1-2 PM at 
 DataLab. After the talk stick around for refreshments during our weekly so
 cial "Data Science Cafe" from 2-3 PM. This event is offered in person. All
  members of the University of California system are welcome to attend. Adv
 ance registration requested but not required! Can’t attend this event? M
 aterials from prior UC Davis DataLab workshops are available on DataLab's 
 website. Check out our workshop schedule for other upcoming trainings. Que
 stions? Email datalab-training@ucdavis.edu. Questions? Contact datalab-tra
 ining@ucdavis.edu.
LOCATION:Shields Library\, 360
URL:https://events.library.ucdavis.edu/event/pop-up-talk-w2026-0213
X-SOURCE:UC Davis Library
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:UC Love Data Week 2026 (February 9-13)
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260213T180000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260214T080000Z
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51959615323411
DESCRIPTION:UC Love Data Week (UCLDW) is a week-long offering of presentat
 ions and workshops from across the University of California focused on all
  things data. All members of the UC community are welcome to attend this f
 ree\, virtual event. See the full schedule by day and register now. With o
 ver 20 presentations and workshops\, whether you’re working with qualita
 tive or quantitative data\, there’s plenty to choose from. This year's t
 opics include: Data visualizationIntegrating AIWorking with data in R and 
 PythonData repositoriesand much more! Workshops taught during UCLDW by UC 
 Davis DataLab and Librarians include: Monday\, 2/9 at 11 AM - Intro to Ope
 nRefine for Data CleaningMonday\, 2/9 at 2 PM - How to Use Data Repository
  FindersWednesday\, 2/11 at 10 AM - How I Slacked at Work and Accidentally
  Built an Automated\, AI Driven ETL PipelineThursday\, 2/12 at 10 AM - Vis
 ualizing data with ggplot for R users (offered in person at DataLab and vi
 a Zoom!) For more information please visit the UC Love Data Week website. 
 Please register with your UC campus email. Zoom links will be emailed to r
 egistered participants.
URL:https://events.library.ucdavis.edu/event/uc-love-data-week-2026-februa
 ry-9-13
X-SOURCE:UC Davis Library
END:VEVENT
